Description: Calculate and extract remote sensing metrics for spatial health analysis.
   This package provides R users with a quick and straightforward way to obtain areal or 
   zonal statistics of key indicators and covariates, ideal for modelling infectious diseases
   within the framework of spatial epidemiology.
